items.title: Bajaj Finance Q2 Preview: Profit, NII expected to rise 23% YoY; strong AUM growth seen
items.description: Bajaj Finance (BAF) is expected to report another steady quarter when it announces its Q2FY26 results, with both profit and net interest income (NII) likely growing around 23% year-on-year, supported by robust loan growth, stable margins, and healthy asset quality across segments.
